These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-1::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: collecting, card-games, drawing, puzzles, hiking, singing, sudoku
There are 7 different nationalities: brazilian, british, chinese, colombian, indonesian, nigerian, spanish
 1. the chinese is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 2. the chinese is on the right of the indonesian##1
 3. the chinese is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is drawing##3
 4. the spanish is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 5. the british is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 6. the brazilian is in the middle##1
 7. the colombian is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person who's hobby is drawing is in an even position##4
 9. the nigerian is in an odd position##4
10. the nigerian is on the left or right of the spanish##3
11. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the nigerian##1
12. the person who's hobby is drawing is the indonesian##1
13. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
14. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is drawing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |    6    |    7    |
| Hobby   | hiking      | drawing      | singing    | sudoku    | card-games | collecting     | puzzles     |
| Nationality   | colombian | indonesian | chinese | brazilian | nigerian   | spanish | british |

