.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-2::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: salsa, gospel, punk, techno, metal, country, pop
7 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, goat, hamster, hedgehog, pony, rat
 1. the fan of punk is on the left or right of the fan of gospel##3
 2. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the fan of techno##3
 3. the owner of the hedgehog is in an odd position##4
 4. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
 5. the fan of metal is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the owner of the pony is the fan of techno##1
 7. the fan of gospel is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 8. the fan of country is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
 9. the fan of techno is the owner of the pony##1
10. the fan of punk is between the owner of the pony and the fan of gospel##2
11. the fan of country is in the middle##1
12. the owner of the rat is on the far left or far right##3
13. the fan of gospel is on the far left or far right##3
14. the fan of pop is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |    3    |     4      |      5      |     6     |   7    |
| Music-Genre   | gospel   | punk | techno | country   | pop | salsa | metal |
| Pet           | hedgehog | cat          | pony    | chinchilla | hamster     | goat      | rat    |

