.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-3::.
There 7 different types of food: artichoke, cucumber, eggplant, kale, kiwi, nectarine, onion
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: epic, spy, martial-arts, drama, satire, disaster, time-travel
 1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 2. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the person eating eggplant##3
 3. the person eating cucumber is on the left or right of the person watching epic movies##3
 4. the person eating cucumber is between the person eating nectarine and the person eating kale##2
 5. the person watching disaster movies is on the left or right of the person watching spy movies##3
 6. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1
 7. the person watching satire movies is in an odd position##4
 8. the person watching epic movies is on the far left##1
 9. the person watching spy movies is the person eating artichoke##1
10. the person eating artichoke is on the far right##1
11. the person watching disaster movies is the person eating onion##1
12. the person watching satire movies is between the person eating eggplant and the person eating onion##2

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |     2     |     3     |    4     |       5        |        6        |     7      |
| Food   | kale        | cucumber  | nectarine | eggplant | kiwi           | onion           | artichoke  |
| Movie-Genre    | epic | drama | time-travel   | martial-arts    | satire | disaster | spy |

