 5. the chinese is in the middle##1
 6. the british is on the far right##1
 7. the electrician is in an odd position##4
 8. the librarian is the british##1
 9. the chinese is on the left of the brazilian##1
10. the canadian is on the left of the pilot##1
11. the german is on the left or right of the electrician##3
12. the electrician is in an odd position##4
13. the chinese is on the right of the photographer##1
14. the canadian is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |    4    |     5     |    6    |    7    |
| Job          | electrician  | pilot | photographer     | writer  | teacher | dressmaker    | librarian  |
| Nationality   | canadian | german  | argentine | chinese | brazilian | russian | british |

