.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-20::.
7 different games are played: scrabble, billiard, snooker, mah-jongg, canasta, bridge, go
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: d&b, disco, dubstep, gospel, hip-hop, metal, punk
 1. the fan of punk is on the left or right of the fan of metal##3
 2. the person playing scrabble is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3
 3. the person playing canasta is on the left or right of the fan of dubstep##3
 4. the fan of hip-hop is on the far left##1
 5. the person playing mah-jongg is the fan of disco##1
 6. the fan of d&b is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 7. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of punk##1
 8. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
 9. the person playing bridge is in an odd position##4
10. the person playing go is on the right of the fan of punk##1
11. the person playing go is on the left or right of the fan of dubstep##3
12. the fan of disco is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |   5    |      6      |    7     |
| Game          | bridge   | snooker | go | scrabble | canasta | billiard | mah-jongg |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | punk      | metal     | dubstep  | gospel | d&b         | disco    |

 